The paper proposes a new architecture for online continual compression, which is relevant for downstream online continual learning tasks and standard learning methods under resource constrained data collection. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and learning (cs.LO).
